Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 10:47:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Widen legal pages to container width; make landing pricing
 interactive

- Privacy/Terms now use the same 1080px container as the rest of the
  site instead of a narrower 820px column, so tables and text breathe
  the same way the rest of the marketing pages do.
- Replace the landing page's static Free/Pro/Org three-card pricing
  with a Free card plus an animated Pro/Org toggle card (sliding pill
  switch, rotating gradient ring, crossfading plan details) matching
  the interaction on the dedicated /pricing page.
- Scatter four more floating "connected resource" chips (Webhook,
  AWS S3, Public API, SendGrid) around the hero banner alongside the
  existing four, so the hero reads as fuller and more alive.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01WK21zjTd6ZeibVA7s3spE6
